features: ✅【UNIVERSAL DESIGN】This full motion TV mount holds up to 110 lbs and fits most 32-70inch TVs with VESA size 75*75mm to 400*400mm.
✅【ADJUSTABLE HEIGHT】Convenient for TV centering, full motion TV wall mount with hook design for easy height adjustment when you feel the TV is low or high after installation.

✅【MULTI VIEW ANGLE】This TV bracket with dual articulating arms includes +5°/-15°tilt, ±45°swivel( maximum swivel angle depends on your TV), and +/-4°post-installation adjustment allowing the perfect TV leveling. This full-motion tv wall bracket can pull out to 15.07” and retract back to 3.43”, and save valuable space and making your house look neater.

✅【EASY INSTALLATION】Installing a TV mount has never been easier. Simple 3-Step Install: 1) Screw the brackets to the TV 2) Bolt the wall plate to the wall 3)Attach your TV to the wall plate. Tips: If you need concrete anchors, please contact us to get it which will be sent from the USA.

✅【PRODUCT INCLUDES】Come with bubble level, 3 pieces pack of cable ties and all standard mounting hardware(►TV Screws: M4*12mm 4pcs, M4*30mm 4pcs, M6*12mm 4pcs, M6*35mm 4pcs, M8*25mm, M8*45mm. ►Spacers: M6*17mm 4pcs, M8*22mm 4pcs, 10mm 4pcs, 2.5mm 8pcs. ►Washers: M4 4pcs, M6 4pcs.), friendly US-based customer service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars thrilled with the results
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the USX MOUNT UL Listed Full Motion TV Wall Mount for my new 65-inch TV, and I am thrilled with the results. The installation process was an absolute breeze, thanks to the clear instructions and user-friendly design. It was a quick and straightforward setup. The included hardware and level made aligning the mount a hassle-free experience, ensuring a secure and perfectly leveled installation.The quality of this wall mount is outstanding. The materials used are sturdy and durable, providing robust support for my sizable 65-inch flat-screen TV. I appreciate the UL listing, which adds an extra layer of confidence in the product's safety and reliability. The build quality gives me peace of mind, knowing that my TV is securely mounted to the wall.The full motion capability of this mount is a game-changer. The arc of motion allows me to find the perfect viewing angle from any part of the room. Whether I'm watching TV from the couch or adjusting it for better visibility in another area, the flexibility is fantastic. The smooth and fluid motion ensures that I can easily tilt, swivel, and extend the TV to achieve the optimal viewing position without any hassle.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome tv mount
reviews.reviewText: If your on the fence about buying a mount look no further this is it. Well made easy to install. Everything is included even a small level to keep it straight. You have alot of movement once you install. Moves side to side,, up and down even tilts. Very strong even has a very accurate templet. I bought 2 and for the price you can't find a better one at any price. 100% thumbs up

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Sturdy, Easy to Install
reviews.reviewText: Very sturdy, not flimsy at all. Comes with a wall-mounting template and plenty of hardware to match the back of your TV. Wall lag bolts were 1/2" X 3-3.5" long to secure into studs. The range of motion is perfect for what I needed. Doesn't move up or down but is able to tilt up/down and wide range of motion to turn the tv right or left.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great all around for mid size TV
reviews.reviewText: I ordered two to be able to move 1 TV back and forth between mounts (1 outdoor) and this works perfectly for that setup.The mount is easy to install, has great tilt and stability and a full range of motion to view from multiple angles. I love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Everything was as advertised. Mount is sturdy and came with all the hardware needed for installation.Only thing is you definitely need two people to screw mount to wall. In the past I have been able to do this part alone but this mount is a lot heavier.Other than that it has been awesome.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for a sturdy mount
reviews.reviewText: I was somewhat skeptical but thought I'd give this mount a try. Installation was straightforward. I was a little annoyed by the sharp edges on some of the holes. All of the necessary hardware was supplied. Movement is adequate although it is not as smooth as other, more expensive, mounts I have had. It was easy to mount a soundbar rack. It was easy to adjust the tilt and level the TV.

reviews.reviewText: Got Mount on wall and 50 inch hung within an hour timeframe. Instructions were easy to read and understand. Most importantly, it included more than enough screws, nets and washers of all shapes and varieties to accommodate any type of brand or model
